commit.message:
Added call me maybe song

- Also reduced frequency of playing star wars because it's really
long

Added emergency left/right turn commands

- Also added more songs

Polished random walk process

- Added app.py, a GUI for initiating and stopping the random walk
- Fixed thread coordination between the randomwalk and the
buzzer
- Added ghostbusters.txt tune

Implemented Buzzer class and song-player

- Supports pitches and durations of pitches
- auto_play.py plays a song on the vehicle's buzzer

Implemented Buzzer class to interact with buzzer

- Supports pitches and durations of pitches

Added mechanics for moving and turning to Vehicle

- Adapted turning and moving tests
- Adapted randomwalk.py

Recalibrated Motor and Vehicle classes

- Motors can now move in either direction at a consistent
speed

Implemented random walk program

- Bug fix in motor.py that prevented motors from stopping
properly
Implemented Vehicle class and a test for it

Initial commit

- Added some working tests for the motors
